pageContext.claim: “Democrats can't impeach a Republican President for crimes committed by Democrats. The facts are ‘pouring’ in. The Greatest Witch Hunt in American History! Congress, go back to work and help us at the Border, with Drug Prices and on Infrastructure.”
pageContext.analysis: Congress can impeach the president for "high crimes and misdemeanors," and the special counsel's report on Trump and Russia seems to lay out evidence that Trump committed the federal crime of obstruction of justice. There's no evidence that Democrats committed the election crimes Trump alleges.
